        </item>
        
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[费解]#经常不吃早餐更易过胖超重#这是真的！✅不吃早餐，身体会在午餐时更加渴望摄入高脂肪、高糖分、高能量的食物，导致午餐吃得更多，更不利于减肥！还有研究...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E6%97%A9%E9%A4%90%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%93%E8%BF%87%E8%83%96%E8%B6%85%E9%87%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E6%97%A9%E9%A4%90%E6%9B%B4%E6%98%93%E8%BF%87%E8%83%96%E8%B6%85%E9%87%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常不吃早餐更易过胖超重#</span></a><br><br>这是真的！✅<br><br>不吃早餐，身体会在午餐时更加渴望摄入高脂肪、高糖分、高能量的食物，导致午餐吃得更多，更不利于减肥！还有研究发现，不吃早餐会刺激胰岛素、皮质醇激素等分泌，导致脂肪组织蓄积增加，容易造成超重肥胖。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>小卫建议，大家在最好在6:30-8:30吃早餐，并且做到品种多类、合理搭配。<br><br>当然，不吃早餐最显著的影响是：饿啊！（影响搬砖进度……<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hlhe70jonyj20m80h2753.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:37:23 GMT</pubDate>
